.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/38608/comment/99207","id":"99207","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=sjones","name":"sjones","key":"sjones","accountId":"557058:f5dce1b0-db45-4dd6-a0e8-3cea5effb5ce","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Steve Jones","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"You can simulate a failure to run the instance by stopping the cluster controller just before launch. This will not work every time so the eucalyptus-cc service should be restarted and once the cluster is enabled the test retried. Obviously you should probably not stop the cluster controller on a shared cloud and this assume the cluster controller is on the host from which the test is run:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n#\r\n# service eucalyptus-cc stop; euca-run-instances emi-72b89b3c\r\nStopping Eucalyptus cluster controller: done.\r\nRESERVATION\tr-0145a106\t000748307737\tdefault\r\nINSTANCE\ti-875dcbc9\temi-72b89b3c\teuca-10-111-77-16.eucalyptus.c-12.autoqa.qa1.eucalyptus-systems.com\teuca-10-111-77-31.eucalyptus.internal\tpending\t\t0\t\tm1.small\t2016-02-12T18:26:44.731Z\tone\t\t\t\tmonitoring-disabled\t10.111.77.16\t10.111.77.31\t\t\tinstance-store\t\t\t\t\thvm\t\t\tsg-e69ed9e2\t\t\t\tx86_64\r\n#\r\n#\r\n# euctl cloud.vmstate.p\r\ncloud.vmstate.pending_time = 60\r\n#\r\n#\r\n# euctl cloud.vmstate.pending_time=5\r\ncloud.vmstate.pending_time = 5\r\n#\r\n#\r\n# euca-describe-instances i-875dcbc9\r\nRESERVATION\tr-0145a106\t000748307737\t\r\nINSTANCE\ti-875dcbc9\temi-72b89b3c\t\t\tterminated\t\t0\t\tm1.small\t2016-02-12T18:26:44.731Z\tone\t\t\t\tmonitoring-disabled\t\t\t\t\tinstance-store\t\t\t\t\thvm\t\t\t\t\t\t\tx86_64\r\n#\r\n#\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nWe should document the new property:\r\n\r\n{code}\r\n#\r\n# euca-describe-properties -v cloud.vmstate.pending_time\r\nwarning: euca-describe-properties is deprecated; use ``euctl'' instead\r\nPROPERTY\tcloud.vmstate.pending_time\t5\t\t\r\nDESCRIPTION\tcloud.vmstate.pending_time\tAmount of time (in minutes) before a pending VM will be terminated.\r\n#\r\n#\r\n{code}","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=sjones","name":"sjones","key":"sjones","accountId":"557058:f5dce1b0-db45-4dd6-a0e8-3cea5effb5ce","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/037fddf6d3bf6d691a448e01136f233a?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dsjones%26avatarId%3D18300%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Steve Jones",